You are analyzing an existing Laravel + jQuery application.

Your task is to study the entire codebase and populate the following documentation files so future AI agents can understand the system without repeatedly scanning the entire project.

## General Rules

* Read all relevant source code before writing.
* Prefer facts from code over assumptions.
* Keep documentation concise but complete.
* Do not document unused code.
* Focus on reducing future context/token usage.
* Update existing files only; do not create new documentation files unless required.

